glish domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert d'Oiley married Robert d'Oiley before 1089, in Europe. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1061–Male":"1061–Surnud","1089–1141":"1089–1141","–Female":"Surnud","before 1089":"enne 1089","1089":"1089","1141":"1141","1061":"1061","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, England":"Tatworth, Somerset, England","Europe":"Europe"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1061–Male":"1061–Kuollut","1089–1141":"1089–1141","–Female":"Kuollut","before 1089":"ennen vuotta 1089","1089":"1089","1141":"1141","1061":"1061","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, England":"Tatworth, Somerset, England","Europe":"Europe"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1061–Male":"1061–Décédé","1089–1141":"1089–1141","–Female":"Décédée","before 1089":"avant 1089","1089":"1089","1141":"1141","1061":"1061","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, England":"Tatworth, Somerset, Angleterre","Europe":"Europe","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert d'Oiley a épousé Robert d'Oiley avant 1089, à Europe. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1061–Male":"1061–Verstorben","1089–1141":"1089–1141","–Female":"Verstorben","before 1089":"vor 1089","1089":"1089","1141":"1141","1061":"1061","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, England":"Tatworth, Somerset, England","Europe":"Europa","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert d'Oiley hat vor 1089 in Europa Robert d'Oiley geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","1061–Male":"1061–Desede","1089–1141":"1089–1141","–Female":"Desede","before 1089":"before 1089","1089":"1089","1141":"1141","1061":"1061","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, England":"Tatworth, Somerset, England","Europe":"Europe"},"hu":{"–":"elhunyt","1061–Male":"1061–elhunyt","1089–1141":"1089–1141","–Female":"elhunyt","before 1089":"1089 előtt","1089":"1089","1141":"1141","1061":"1061","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, E